MuiTypography-gutterBottom">Get to know this product.<!-- --> <span class="jss406"></span></h2><div class="jss429" id="product-overview-section"><div class="MuiPaper-root MuiAccordion-root Mui-expanded MuiAccordion-rounded MuiPaper-elevation1 MuiPaper-rounded"><h3 aria-controls="Product Overview-content" aria-disabled="false" aria-expanded="true" class="MuiButtonBase-root MuiAccordionSummary-root jss430 jss431 Mui-expanded" role="button" tabindex="0"><div class="MuiAccordionSummary-content Mui-expanded">Product Overview</div><div aria-disabled="false" aria-hidden="true" class="MuiButtonBase-root MuiIconButton-root MuiAccordionSummary-expandIcon Mui-expanded MuiIconButton-edgeEnd"><span class="MuiIconButton-label"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="MuiSvgIcon-root" focusable="false" viewbox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6z"></path></svg></span><span class="MuiTouchRipple-root"></span></div></h3><div class="MuiCollapse-root MuiCollapse-entered" style="min-height:0px"><div class="MuiCollapse-wrapper"><div class="MuiCollapse-wrapperInner"><div id="Product Overview-content" role="region"><div class="MuiAccordionDetails-root jss432"><div class="jss433"><div class="jss434"><h4 class="MuiTypography-root jss435 MuiTypography-h5">Product Overview</h4><h6 aria-level="5" class="MuiTypography-root jss438 MuiTypography-subtitle1" data-uw-rm-heading="level" role="heading">Dual Power Filtration</h6><p class="MuiTypography-root jss437 MuiTypography-body1">Skip soaking, scrubbing and prerinsing with Maytag engineering that puts an end to pre-work. Industry-exclusive Dual Power filtration combines microfiltration and a 4-blade stainless steel chopper to filter out then disintegrate any food in its path.</p><h6 class="MuiTypography-root jss438 MuiTypography-subtitle1">3rd Level Rack</h6><p class="MuiTypography-root jss437 MuiTypography-body1">Put more than utensils in the Maytag 3rd Level Rack. With a specialized wash zone and room for mugs and bowls, this distinct design brings more loading space and cleaning power straight to the top of the dishwasher.</p><h6 class="MuiTypography-root jss438 MuiTypography-subtitle1">PowerBlast Cycle</h6><p class="MuiTypography-root jss437 MuiTypography-body1">The PowerBlast cycle scours away stubborn foods like egg yolk, peanut butter and even dried-on oatmeal. High-pressure jets, increased water temperatures and hot steam work together to clear food off dishesso all you have to do is load them in.</p><h6 class="MuiTypography-root jss438 MuiTypography-subtitle1">Touch Controls</h6><p class="MuiTypography-root jss437 MuiTypography-body1">Youre in control with a simple tap of your finger. Smooth, tap-to-activate settings give you quick and seamless access to powerful cleaning.</p><h6 class="MuiTypography-root jss438 MuiTypography-subtitle1">Cast Iron Black</h6><p class="MuiTypography-root jss437 MuiTypography-body1">Cast Iron Black is a finely textured, matte finish inspired by iconiccast iron. Its as tough as it is timelessengineered to stand up toeveryday scratches, minor dents and fingerprints that build up overtime.</p><h6 class="MuiTypography-root jss438 MuiTypography-subtitle1">Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel</h6><p class="MuiTypography-root jss437 MuiTypography-body1">Easy-to-clean, fingerprint resistant stainless steel resists smudges and streaks to keep your dishwasher looking as good on the outside as it works on the inside.</p><h6 class="MuiTypography-root jss438 MuiTypography-subtitle1">10-Year Limited Parts Warranty on the Racks, Chopper Blade and Stainless Steel Tub</h6><p class="MuiTypography-root jss437 MuiTypography-body1">Maytag dishwashers are covered by a 10-year limited parts warranty on the racks, chopper blade and stainless steel tub. So when we say you can count on your dishwasher for years, we mean it.</p><h6 class="MuiTypography-root jss438 MuiTypography-subtitle1">Premium Ball-Bearing Rack Glides</h6><p class="MuiTypography-root jss437 MuiTypography-body1">Our premium ball-bearing rack glides give the upper rack a glide so smooth you can pull it out even when youre hauling an armload of bowls, or when the rack's lugging your heaviest dishes and baking pans.</p><h6 class="MuiTypography-root jss438 MuiTypography-subtitle1">Built for the Long Haul</h6><p class="MuiTypography-root jss437 MuiTypography-body1">We packed in sturdy stainless steel thats ready for cycle after cycle of tough cleaning. Built for high heat and less likely to crack than plastic, stainless steel materials also resist stains to help keep your dishwasher looking good for years to come.</p><h6 class="MuiTypography-root jss438 MuiTypography-subtitle1">Steam Sanitize Option</h6><p class="MuiTypography-root jss437 MuiTypography-body1">The Steam Sanitize option lets you confidently wash important items with a high-temperature rinse that removes 99.999% of food soil bacteria.</p><h6 class="MuiTypography-root jss438 MuiTypography-subtitle1">Full Stainless Steel Tub</h6><p class="MuiTypography-root jss437 MuiTypography-body1">The full stainless steel tub is built of stainless steel from top to bottom, so its tough enough to handle high heat and resist cracking and staining for years.</p><h6 class="MuiTypography-root jss438 MuiTypography-subtitle1">End-of-Cycle Indicator</h6><p class="MuiTypography-root jss437 MuiTypography-body1">The end-of-cycle indicator lets you know exactly where the dishwasher is in the wash cycle: when it's in process, when its finished and when the Steam Sanitize option is in use.</p></div><div class="jss434"><h5 class="MuiTypography-root jss435 fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></div><span></span></div><h2 id="ot-pc-title">Privacy Preference Center</h2><div id="ot-pc-desc">When you visit any website, it may store or retrieve information on your browser, mostly in the form of cookies. This information might be about you, your preferences or your device and is mostly used to make the site work as you expect it to. The information does not usually directly identify you, but it can give you a more personalized web experience. Because we respect your right to privacy, you can choose not to allow some types of cookies. Click on the different category headings to find out more and change our default settings. However, blocking some types of cookies may impact your experience of the site and the services we are able to offer.
            <br/><a aria-label="More information about your privacy, opens in a new tab" class="privacy-notice-link" data-uw-original-href="https://cookiepedia.co.uk/giving-consent-to-cookies" data-uw-rm-brl="PR" data-uw-rm-ext-link="na" href="https://cookiepedia.co.uk/giving-consent-to-cookies" rel="noopener" target="_blank">More information</a></div><button id="accept-recommended-btn-handler">Allow All</button><section class="ot-sdk-row ot-cat-grp"><h3 id="ot-category-title"> Manage Consent Preferences</h3><div class="ot-accordion-layout ot-cat-item ot-vs-config" data-optanongroupid="C0003"><button aria-controls="ot-desc-id-C0003" aria-expanded="false" aria-labelledby="ot-header-id-C0003" ot-accordion="true"></button><!-- Accordion header --><div class="ot-acc-hdr"><div class="ot-plus-minus"><span></span><span></span></div><h4 class="ot-cat-header" id="ot-header-id-C0003">Functional Cookies</h4><div class="ot-tgl"><input aria-labelledby="ot-header-id-C0003" class="category-switch-handler" data-optanongroupid="C0003" data-uw-rm-form="nfx" id="ot-group-id-C0003" name="ot-group-id-C0003" role="switch" type="checkbox"/> <label class="ot-switch" for="ot-group-id-C0003"><span class="ot-switch-nob"></span> <span class="ot-label-txt">Functional Cookies</span></label> </div></div><!-- accordion detail --><div class="ot-acc-grpcntr ot-acc-txt"><p class="ot-acc-grpdesc ot-category-desc" id="ot-desc-id-C0003">These cookies enable the website to provide enhanced functionality and personalisation. They may be set by us or by third party providers whose services we have added to our pages. If you do not allow these cookies then some or all of these services may not function properly.</p></div></div><div class="ot-accordion-layout ot-cat-item ot-vs-config" data-optanongroupid="C0005"><button aria-controls="ot-desc-id-C0005" aria-expanded="false" aria-labelledby="ot-header-id-C0005" ot-accordion="true"></button><!-- Accordion header --><div class="ot-acc-hdr"><div class="ot-plus-minus"><span></span><span></span></div><h4 class="ot-cat-header" id="ot-header-id-C0005">Social Media Cookies</h4><div class="ot-tgl"><input aria-labelledby="ot-header-id-C0005" class="category-switch-handler" data-optanongroupid="C0005" data-uw-rm-form="nfx" id="ot-group-id-C0005" name="ot-group-id-C0005" role="switch" type="checkbox"/> <label class="ot-switch" for="ot-group-id-C0005"><span class="ot-switch-nob"></span> <span class="ot-label-txt">Social Media Cookies</span></label> </div></div><!-- accordion detail --><div class="ot-acc-grpcntr ot-acc-txt"><p class="ot-acc-grpdesc ot-category-desc" id="ot-desc-id-C0005">These cookies are set by a range of social media services that we have added to the site to enable you to share our content with your friends and networks. They are capable of tracking your browser across other sites and building up a profile of your interests. This may impact the content and messages you see on other websites you visit. If you do not allow these cookies you may not be able to use or see these sharing tools.</p></div></div><div class="ot-accordion-layout ot-cat-item ot-vs-config" data-optanongroupid="C0004"><button aria-controls="ot-desc-id-C0004" aria-expanded="false" aria-labelledby="ot-header-id-C0004" ot-accordion="true"></button><!-- Accordion header --><div class="ot-acc-hdr"><div class="ot-plus-minus"><span></span><span></span></div><h4 class="ot-cat-header" id="ot-header-id-C0004">Targeting Cookies</h4><div class="ot-tgl"><input aria-labelledby="ot-header-id-C0004" class="category-switch-handler" data-optanongroupid="C0004" data-uw-rm-form="nfx" id="ot-group-id-C0004" name="ot-group-id-C0004" role="switch" type="checkbox"/> <label class="ot-switch" for="ot-group-id-C0004"><span class="ot-switch-nob"></span> <span class="ot-label-txt">Targeting Cookies</span></label> </div></div><!-- accordion detail --><div class="ot-acc-grpcntr ot-acc-txt"><p class="ot-acc-grpdesc ot-category-desc" id="ot-desc-id-C0004">These cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant adverts on other sites. They do not store directly personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser and internet device. If you do not allow these cookies, you will experience less targeted advertising.</p></div></div><div class="ot-accordion-layout ot-cat-item ot-vs-config" data-optanongroupid="C0002"><button aria-controls="ot-desc-id-C0002" aria-expanded="false" aria-labelledby="ot-header-id-C0002" ot-accordion="true"></button><!-- Accordion header --><div class="ot-acc-hdr"><div class="ot-plus-minus"><span></span><span></span></div><h4 class="ot-cat-header" id="ot-header-id-C0002">Performance Cookies</h4><div class="ot-tgl"><input aria-labelledby="ot-header-id-C0002" class="category-switch-handler" data-optanongroupid="C0002" data-uw-rm-form="nfx" id="ot-group-id-C0002" name="ot-group-id-C0002" role="switch" type="checkbox"/> <label class="ot-switch" for="ot-group-id-C0002"><span class="ot-switch-nob"></span> <span class="ot-label-txt">Performance Cookies</span></label> </div></div><!-- accordion detail --><div class="ot-acc-grpcntr ot-acc-txt"><p class="ot-acc-grpdesc ot-category-desc" id="ot-desc-id-C0002">These cookies allow us to count visits and traffic sources so we can measure and improve the performance of our site. They help us to know which pages are the most and least popular and see how visitors move around the site. All information these cookies collect is aggregated and therefore anonymous. If you do not allow these cookies we will not know when you have visited our site, and will not be able to monitor its performance.</p></div></div><div class="ot-accordion-layout ot-cat-item ot-vs-config" data-optanongroupid="C0001"><button aria-controls="ot-desc-id-C0001" aria-expanded="false" aria-labelledby="ot-header-id-C0001 ot-status-id-C0001" ot-accordion="true"></button><!-- Accordion header --><div class="ot-acc-hdr ot-always-active-group"><div class="ot-plus-minus"><span></span><span></span></div><h4 class="ot-cat-header" id="ot-header-id-C0001">Strictly Necessary Cookies</h4><div class="ot-always-active" id="ot-status-id-C0001">Always Active</div></div><!-- accordion detail --><div class="ot-acc-grpcntr ot-acc-txt"><p class="ot-acc-grpdesc ot-category-desc" id="ot-desc-id-C0001">These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be switched off in our systems. They are usually only set in response to actions made by you which amount to a request for services, such as setting your privacy preferences, logging in or filling in forms. You can set your browser to block or alert you about these cookies, but some parts of the site will not then work.
